# Design Philosophy

Every major capability must remain replaceable.

Examples:

Scene Detection

OCR

LLM Provider

Embedding Provider

Storage

Export

Future providers should require minimal code changes.

---

# Fireworks

Fireworks is the current AI provider.

Fireworks must only be accessed through:

FireworksClient

No other module should communicate directly with Fireworks.

---

# Backend Philosophy

Routes remain thin.

Business logic belongs in services.

Services communicate through abstractions.

Configuration controls behaviour.

No hardcoded values.

---

# Frontend Philosophy

Frontend displays state.

Frontend never performs AI processing.

Frontend never performs business logic.

Frontend communicates only through backend APIs.

---

